				\begin{document}$$X_0$$\end{document} and Z0\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$Z_0$$\end{document} and a parameter characterizing the efficacy of convection (see Sect. 2.5). This adjustment constitutes the calibration of solar models.

