				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${{}^{8}\mathrm{B}}$$\end{document}. In all cases the hatched regions indicate the 1σ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
