These changes in the solar model have had a drastic effect on the comparison with the helioseismic results. An extensive review of these consequences was provided by Basu and Antia (2008), while a more recent, but brief, review is in Serenelli (2016). The maximum relative change in c2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
